{"tid":22043,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡咖啡教學","createTime":"2016-12-04T08:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T15:13:59.000Z","uid":1567,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb46ea4c7107a43323d77fe1fd41b07fc3d07adb","tid":22043,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:04:33.000Z","msg":"黎新加坡旅遊，一定要去下kopitiam嘆咖啡<br />\n但首先要學識點樣買一杯咖啡︰<br />\n<br />\nkopi: 咖啡<br />\nteh: 奶茶<br />\no: 走奶<br />\nc: 轉淡奶<br />\nkosong: 走糖<br />\nsiew dai: 少糖<br />\nga dai: 加糖<br />\npeng: 加冰<br />\ngao: 厚咖啡<br />\npo: 薄咖啡<br />\nsua: 雙份<br />\nta pao: 打包<br />\n<br />\n例子: kopi o kosong ta bao=黑咖啡走糖拎走<br />\n<br />\n另外新加坡亦有其他特色飲品︰<br />\nteh tarik: 拉茶<br />\ntak giu: 米祿<br />\nmilo dinosaur: 米褖恐龍<br />\nbandung: 玫瑰奶<br />\ntiao he: 中國茶<br />\nchin chow: 仙草水<br />\n<br />\n諗到再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f74edfdbaddbbc8de9f5b28c055e135e16156fd","tid":22043,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ae126e2cc880fdbdba632bb87bcbe94fc62316fc","tid":22043,"uid":34284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pk5r2qdi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpk5r2qdi&h=7c0ebfe9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5e7058374c27a5c41a60ad68994aeca536bc10b","tid":22043,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/pk5r2qdi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpk5r2qdi&h=7c0ebfe9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老老實實我覺fun toast d野好食過亞坤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660ac8faf2b5900ae5084915f095526e0b100125","tid":22043,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB